      "body_text": "*We do not have enough information to find the cause of this issue.*\\n\\nPlease attach the full launcher log from when this issue occurred. You can find it in the `.minecraft` directory, named `launcher_log.txt`.\\n\\nAlso, please provide us with your system specifications. To do so, launch a version of the game unaffected by this issue, take a screenshot of your debug screen (enabled by pressing the F3 key) and attach it to this report.\\n\\n**Quick Links:**📓 Bug Tracker Guidelines – 💬 Community Support – 📧 Mojang Support (Technical Issues) – 📧 Microsoft Support (Account Issues)📓 Project Summary – ✍️ Feedback and Suggestions – 📖 Game Wiki\\n\\n",
      "body_length": 646,
      "rendered_body": "<p><em>We do not have enough information to find the cause of this issue.</em></p>\n\n<p>Please attach the full launcher log from when this issue occurred. You can find it in the <a href=\"https://minecrafthopper.net/help/finding-minecraft-data-folder/\" class=\"external-link\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><tt>.minecraft</tt></a> directory, named <tt>launcher_log.txt</tt>.</p>\n\n<p>Also, please provide us with your system specifications. To do so, launch a version of the game unaffected by this issue, take a screenshot of your debug screen (enabled by pressing the F3 key) and attach it to this report.</p>\n\n<p><b>Quick Links:</b><br>\n📓 <a href=\"https://aka.ms/MCBugTrackerHelp\" class=\"external-link\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Bug Tracker Guidelines</a> – 💬 <a href=\"https://discord.com/invite/58Sxm23\" class=\"external-link\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Community Support</a> – 📧 <a href=\"https://aka.ms/Minecraft-Support\" class=\"external-link\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Mojang Support (Technical Issues)</a> – 📧 <a href=\"https://support.xbox.com/contact-us/\" class=\"external-link\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Microsoft Support (Account Issues)</a><br>\n📓 <a href=\"https://report.bugs.mojang.com/servicedesk/customer/portal/2\" class=\"external-link\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Project Summary</a> – ✍️ <a href=\"https://aka.ms/MinecraftFeedbackDiscord\" class=\"external-link\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Feedback and Suggestions</a> – 📖 <a href=\"https://minecraft.wiki\" class=\"external-link\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Game Wiki</a></p>",
